{"tid":266233,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔見銀包..","createTime":"2017-06-01T09:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T13:48:18.000Z","uid":61,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e167c975b4d6e3ce727a7d41a7f53857d660829","tid":266233,"uid":61,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:47:52.000Z","msg":"今日15:30-33分係58M向良景方向,盈豐站落車...<br />\n落車後發現唔見銀包,跑返去良景總站仲差D俾輕鐵撞..<br />\n去到良景站頭沖上車搵已經搵唔返...問站頭又無,<br />\n入邊得兩張今日返實習公司出嘅支票,70元,身份證銀行卡等等<br />\n<br />\n款式係拉鍊款藍黑色....porter牌(家姐送的生日禮物)<br />\n如有拾獲,希望能當可憐我交去就近警署或聯絡我<br />\n<br />\n因為時間太急...個入境處網太廢入唔到去預約...點樣可以出到境...<br />\n19號就要上機...點算...心急人上"},{"pid":"eebe3f18b25d7420dc35789757d65e04f80045e1","tid":266233,"uid":61,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:51:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/Klongo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FKlongo&d=X1LzviS17SySsPZJwcPYbwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=0416a56f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Klongo</a>"},{"pid":"85a41d8dfd2fa304b19a6a1667a55f26fca001e5","tid":266233,"uid":61,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:51:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b48b47e2303b62fd1652dcba900ca34a08febc1c","tid":266233,"uid":61,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:51:35.000Z","msg":"求好心人...."},{"pid":"107b9ada242f970fa1dd345b3d5785556a260486","tid":266233,"uid":61,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:51:52.000Z","msg":"連登很好多好心巴打我相信..."},{"pid":"93c090d63b0036846be05c74d8fe6f4e7689ace9","tid":266233,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:54:42.000Z","msg":"幫你推下啦 <br />\n連登有鬼好人咩 之前都試過 連幫推嘅人都冇 死心啦"},{"pid":"c4c36d6d18786c20f1c7602dc4c40e1cd55cfbde","tid":266233,"uid":34075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:56:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫你推下"},{"pid":"2dd77c4ce4